                        <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/3387: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Consul at Geneva</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Gilbert</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-11-11T14:00:00-05:00">November 11, 1933—2
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>124. Your telegram 287, November 8, 4 p.m., paragraph 4. Please keep the
                            Department informed of important developments.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi></signed></closer>
